# 1D MHD Linear Wave problems

REQUIRES Driver
REQUIRES physics/Eos/EosMain/Gamma
REQUIRES physics/Hydro

D sim_wave  Which type of wave
PARAMETER sim_wave STRING "alfven" ["alfven", "fast", "slow"]

D sim_dir  Direction of propagation for wave, -1 for left, +1 for right
D sim_amp  Amplitude of the perturbation wave
D sim_len  Wavelength of the perturbation wave
PARAMETER sim_amp  REAL     1.e-6  [0 to ]
PARAMETER sim_len  REAL     1.0    [0 to ]
PARAMETER sim_dir  INTEGER  1      [-1,1]


D sim_dens Initial mass density
D sim_pres Initial pressure
PARAMETER sim_dens  REAL 1.0  [0 to ]
PARAMETER sim_pres  REAL 0.6  [0 to ]

D sim_vx Initial velocity in the x-direction
D sim_vy Initial velocity in the y-direction
D sim_vz Initial velocity in the z-direction
PARAMETER sim_velx  REAL 0.0
PARAMETER sim_vely  REAL 0.0
PARAMETER sim_velz  REAL 0.0


D sim_Bx Magnetic field vector in x-direction
D sim_By Magnetic field vector in y-direction
D sim_Bz Magnetic field vectory in z-direction
PARAMETER sim_magx      REAL 1.
PARAMETER sim_magy      REAL 1.41421356237
PARAMETER sim_magz      REAL 0.5

